Package com.i2group.disco.audit

Interface IUserUpdateAuditEvent

All Superinterfaces:
IAuditEvent, IUserInfo
public interface IUserUpdateAuditEvent extends IUserInfo, IAuditEvent
An event that was generated during the processing of an "update user" provisioning operation. IUserUpdateAuditEvent makes information about the operation available to the audit logging mechanism.
